22
00:04:41.049 --> 00:04:43.426
No. The Hinchberger wedding.

23
00:04:43.427 --> 00:04:44.886
Hinchberger wedding.

24
00:04:45.929 --> 00:04:49.724
Tuxedos. droning conversations.
I don't think so. No.

25
00:04:49.725 --> 00:04:51.101
