40
00:05:27.430 --> 00:05:30.557
I tried to assure him that you
were very busy... What's his name?

41
00:05:30.558 --> 00:05:32.435
A Mr. Seymour Butts.

42
00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:37.356
Under the Bleachers
by Seymour Butts.

43
00:05:38.024 --> 00:05:39.442
