65
00:06:36.750 --> 00:06:37.834
You look good.

66
00:06:37.876 --> 00:06:38.918
So do you.

67
00:06:38.919 --> 00:06:40.128
To think I was worried.

68
00:06:40.879 --> 00:06:42.338
Worried about me?

69
00:06:42.339 --> 00:06:45.425
