108
00:08:15.767 --> 00:08:17.393
An escort service?

109
00:08:18.353 --> 00:08:20.647
A profound life experience.

110
00:08:22.190 --> 00:08:23.941
Sorry. I'll just...

111
00:08:23.942 --> 00:08:25.401
No. that's all right. Just...

112
00:08:26.945 --> 00:08:28.278
Tell me you'll call.

113
