163
00:12:04.040 --> 00:12:05.708
I've always liked your brother.

164
00:12:07.043 --> 00:12:08.586
Anyway...

165
00:12:08.711 --> 00:12:10.378
I... I just thought

166
00:12:10.379 --> 00:12:11.963
