difficult for you...

167
00:12:11.964 --> 00:12:13.591
Just another birthday.

168
00:12:14.675 --> 00:12:16.636
Because of your father.

169
00:12:17.303 --> 00:12:19.346
That's right.
He was 48. wasn't he?

170
00:12:19.347 --> 00:12:21.849
I hadn't really thought
