here somewhere.

213
00:15:19.529 --> 00:15:21.239
You mind holding that?

214
00:15:22.824 --> 00:15:24.284
Thank you very much.

215
00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:28.330
Thank you.

216
00:15:28.455 --> 00:15:30.289
